POST https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1
Host: api.openai.com
User-Agent: langchaingo-httprr
Content-Length: 3230
Authorization: Bearer test-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{"model":"gpt-4.1-nano","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Write a concise summary of the following:\n\n\n\"\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver, a curious mouse from a peaceful village in an enchanted forest, longs for adventure and new friendships beyond his usual surroundings.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver, a brave mouse, set out on a sunny morning with cheese and a walking stick to find new friends who shared his love for adventure.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver explored the forest, excited by the flora and birds, and discovered a sunny pond in a clearing.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver encounters Leo, a regal and gentle lion, by the pond and joyfully invites him to be his friend.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eLeo, a brave and curious lion, warmly greets Oliver the mouse and offers to join him on his noble quest, fostering a bond of friendship.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver's adventure with Leo expanded as they explored meadows, trees, and rivers, meeting Freddie the frog, a talented hopper and treasure finder.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eFreddie, an emerald-skinned frog, joins Oliver, Leo, and others on their adventure, forming a strong bond filled with laughter and friendship, bringing joy and camaraderie to their journey.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eThe friends encounter a volcano and a menacing lava monster, prompting Oliver to devise a clever plan to confront it.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver urges his friends, Leo and Freddie, to collaborate—Leo distracts the monster, Freddie navigates the terrain, and they plan to find and exploit its weakness together.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eLeo, Freddie, and Oliver fought a lava monster, discovering its weak spot—a gem in its chest. They struck it, causing the monster to disintegrate, and the forest was saved.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver, Leo, and Freddie's victory led to a celebration in the enchanted forest, where a mouse's journey to find friends revealed the true meaning of friendship and made him a hero.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver, Leo, and Freddie became close friends whose adventures and kindness inspired others, demonstrating that true friendship transcends all differences.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdocument\u003e\n\u003ccontent\u003eOliver's story of magic, friendship, and bravery became a timeless legend, cherished by generations of forest dwellers.\u003c/content\u003e\n\n\u003c/document\u003e\n\"\n\n\nCONCISE SUMMARY:"}]}HTTP/2.0 200 OK
